{"type": "article", "id": 25961, "title": "像棚内照明的灯具系列", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-26T07:35:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140244dpbIlHiR6CUhYV5B.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.leklint.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Le Klint</a> 旗下的这组看上去像专业摄影棚内照明的灯具系列名叫 Carronade，由 <a href=\"http://markusjohansson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Markus Johansson Design Studio</a> 设计。这一系列灯具包括：落地灯、桌灯和小型装饰灯，黑色的金属支架搭配胡桃木和黄铜组件。时尚大方的外型无论是在办公还是居家场所都非常适用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140242hVpmNEjPA4OqSwXy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140242LXR2oequit9PHcAQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.23166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021402433OSVwlxmFcEAgB9n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140243HzcGLAikTn895w2I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}